{"tid":1917200,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"Pi幣","createTime":"2020-03-09T10:51:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T08:20:14.000Z","uid":198216,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0b5e67700eb1f500d10d3546c028b39ce7feeceb","tid":1917200,"uid":198216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T10:51:58.000Z","msg":"點睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n瑞波幣5元變一億，耗時3年。<br />\n比特幣5元變一億，耗時8年。<br />\n小蟻幣11萬變一億，耗時2年。<br />\n以太坊2萬變一億，耗時3年。<br />\n還有萊特幣等等，這些幣有一個共同點，就是開始時候都是免費挖的、免費的、免費的、免費的。<br />\n<br />\n今天的Pi 也是，並且剛剛開始!!!<br />\n全球性主流幣，斯坦福大學出身，或許又將會創造奇跡，斯坦福大學被譽為硏究數字貨幣的聖地。瑞波幣和恆星幣也是出自斯坦福大學。<br />\n<br />\n註冊連結：IOS下載連結：<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/pi-network/id1445472541\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fpi-network%2Fid1445472541&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FM8wxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=a19086b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/us/app/pi-network/id1445472541</a><br />\n<br />\nAndroid下載連結：<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.blockchainvault\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.blockchainvault&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FM8wxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=e2a4c60a\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.blockchainvault</a><br />\n<br />\n一般用戶一天約可挖出《11~50顆 pi 幣》所以，不挖白不挖，有挖就有機會，預估2年之內一顆pi 幣價值可達10-50美金或以上更高的價值。<br />\n<br />\n（申請步驟如下）<br />\n台灣和香港用FB臉書註冊即可，(其它國家用手機註冊)<br />\n<br />\nLast Name：姓氏（實名）<br />\nFirst Name：名字（實名）<br />\nUser Name：自行取名自己的使用者名稱<br />\n<br />\n填入邀請碼 <br />\nInvitation code ：hk721831101<br />\n<br />\n最後步驟：點擊閃電符號變綠色即可"},{"pid":"710a67447ec7ad31bac34bd294401d019bf1c763","tid":1917200,"uid":324712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T10:56:52.000Z","msg":"玩完做斃少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/de